com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.processor

Class GenProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.annotation.processing.AbstractProcessor
      • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.annotation.processor.GenProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenDispatchProcessor, GenDtoProcessor, GenEventProcessor, GenProxyProcessor

    public abstract class GenProcessor
extends AbstractProcessor

    Abstract processor class for all @GenX annotations.

    Annotate your processor with @SupportedAnnotationTypes or override AbstractProcessor.getSupportedAnnotationTypes() to receive elements, that are annotated in the current environment with one of the given annotations. You can get access these elements using the method process(Element annotatedElement).

    Author:
    Florian Sauter
